{"tid":2105100,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（集思廣益）詢求關於製作關於陳志祥遊戲的意見","createTime":"2020-07-12T11:49:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T23:13:16.000Z","uid":38861,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"db0e300422b66397f83994faf0ddd1f0e848846a","tid":2105100,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T11:49:39.000Z","msg":"是咁的，前排的起心肝學製作遊戲同畫畫，希望可以獨自整一隻遊戲出嚟，免費俾所有人玩。<br />\n<br />\n暫時隻遊戲名暫定為Grand Theft Melon721，大致個遊戲框架都整得七七八八，但美術等等仲係努力緊。 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i5nome2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi5nome2.png&h=e7b45050&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊戲背景係講陳志祥逃逸香港到外地，喺721一週年當日打俾警署一哥，話見事件有淡化之勢可唔可以俾佢暗度返番香港，理由係好掛住啲香港的西瓜同埋想親自打理番自己的逢吉農場（前身又名小牛農場）。<br />\n<br />\n一哥起初是拒絕的，但最後作出忍讓，同陳志祥講只要空運幾十個極品西瓜到警署，而一眾警隊成員對西瓜感到滿意的話，就批准佢暗度返番黎香港。<br />\n<br />\n正因為咁，陳志祥再操舊業，開始番耕田工作，而遊戲最終目的就係種出傳說中的極品西瓜，獲取返港機票。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好初步的遊戲圖，仲有大量美術等等要執：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/My9Rvby.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMy9Rvby.png&h=708ef336&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F28KQbO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF28KQbO.png&h=c5cf12a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8LXfWRT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8LXfWRT.png&h=c38db760&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n製作其間想係度收集一下意見，各位巴絲想裡頭有咩內容或者系統？"},{"pid":"8b38fc5c39b30cc5807f9987804f45ddddd09219","tid":2105100,"uid":49707,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T11:50:24.000Z","msg":"lm等玩"},{"pid":"26b77ff1cf4dd5c5f1f4514f29d1887522c75d66","tid":2105100,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T11:57:40.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc448d1982f7a46d99b225b385301834b84f600","tid":2105100,"uid":10453,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T11:58:31.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"7c5cda0616b572c2434ac287ebb29b89d03ec121","tid":2105100,"uid":300782,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T11:58:39.000Z","msg":"有人搶西瓜 要斬人 保護西瓜"},{"pid":"2e76c96c7f378164dcc28248a74400f3fa72b758","tid":2105100,"uid":155238,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T11:59:49.000Z","msg":"有無得種薯仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f05f58274d6059686fefe3a14f0721962e99233","tid":2105100,"uid":38861,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c5cda0616b572c2434ac287ebb29b89d03ec121","tid":2105100,"uid":300782,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T11:58:39.000Z","msg":"有人搶西瓜 要斬人 保護西瓜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T12:00:36.000Z","msg":"我有諗過一個主意係間唔中會有毒蛇搶西瓜，要買黃色頭盔鑰匙扣擺地下嚇走啲蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5ba5edd2c1b3cbc42ecb8909c94abceb8002a9","tid":2105100,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e76c96c7f378164dcc28248a74400f3fa72b758","tid":2105100,"uid":155238,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T11:59:49.000Z","msg":"有無得種薯仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T12:01:23.000Z","msg":"有，當然，而且一定係遊戲入面賣得最貴的農作物。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50607a0fe82509b9ef66721d168f7363fae76e50","tid":2105100,"uid":174441,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T12:01:28.000Z","msg":"睇左羅志祥"},{"pid":"7f34496e404070dc15512e620f77410e560730f9","tid":2105100,"uid":199700,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T12:04:13.000Z","msg":"買完機票翻到香港之後要俾手足火魔燒到十成熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28bddc4f918077cde14b8dd563865891983fc6e7","tid":2105100,"uid":3